89,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T08:17:33.000Z","msg":"Google左，應該得兩大集團<br />\n<br />\n一係撚賤，一係就同姓董果條廢老同名<br />\n<br />\n開名啦屌"},{"pid":"53a20c1c74ff9d958f544e9cd2317f92a0128b29","tid":2130313,"uid":88743,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1d2575aebdce9708ad367ed205be2971e2adf4ec","tid":2130313,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1e026ec7f02b39727f2940684973f787e66851c9","tid":2130313,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d464b10638111c8a135ea637aacd7b90c34fa94c","tid":2130313,"uid":231886,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:45:18.000Z","msg":"網民一早講緊，咁關白兵咩事？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:58:19.000Z","msg":"白兵-&gt;公海-&gt;白兵-&gt;公海"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T08:03:44.000Z","msg":"白兵最早幾時講先？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T08:22:00.000Z","msg":"我淨係知白兵拍左段片講健康碼有幾咁仆街<br />\n段片白痴都聽得明健康碼有幾咁惡<br />\n應該係我見過第一條片係講健康碼, 唔洗再睇連登千字文先理解到係乜黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tHeE6zjhFl4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtHeE6zjhFl4&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6fzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=00b8583a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tHeE6zjhFl4</a><br />\n<br />\n仲講埋點用DNA監控<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kbqcNcRHioM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkbqcNcRHioM&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6fzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=5b3f902e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kbqcNcRHioM</a><br />\n<br />\n但連登就因為私怨 逢白兵必反<br />\n好撚多師奶唔撚知健康碼有幾咁仆街就多得你地班撚屌唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091c19000afe228f0fe89ec356aee908e9265ae6","tid":2130313,"uid":23968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T08:23:57.000Z","msg":"求奇post 張圖就當係 fc 呢？"},{"pid":"8992e8aad17bb5269f3d8b212716e9c94151ebe4","tid":2130313,"uid":205967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T08:36:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我淨係知白兵拍左段片講健康碼有幾咁仆街<br />\n段片白痴都聽得明健康碼有幾咁惡<br />\n應該係我見過第一條片係講健康碼,<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">唔洗再睇連登千字文先理解到係乜黎</span></span><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你自己都認咗連登有人一早講咗，但死都要讚白兵 。<br />\n字多就唔睇，最多咪得個4000字，有幾多啊？咁你點讀書睇書？下下要人用把口講你知你先知，又唔自己睇news。<br />\n做打手做到你咁自爆自己係文盲，我都係第一個見，定你係本人？<br />\n同埋班師奶要信嘅點都會信，你俾news佢睇佢都會睇，同埋一早有文宣圖出咗，自己鍾意睇佢啲片就認啦，唔駛屈落其他人到。<br />\nbtw 我依到有700字多啲，希望你睇曬先駁我"},{"pid":"8b968bff1a7f84f8e44a6decb752b03f64e7afb5","tid":2130313,"uid":193834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c763fc97a5b83977997b717bae117f4cd1fadd8b","tid":2130313,"uid":131522,"like":36,"dislike":4,"score":32,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:49:30.000Z","msg":"本司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T08:56:35.000Z","msg":"重有，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">我司</span></span>"},{"pid":"1cc5fff6fe1609ae24cedee814f8839291da72b5","tid":2130313,"uid":323228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86b378223806c53df6895688a9f03d24c111525d","tid":2130313,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:46:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dixetX5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdixetX5.jpg&h=b16932b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/109087273779959/posts/311440200211331/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F109087273779959%2Fposts%2F311440200211331%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6fzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=3609924e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/109087273779959/posts/311440200211331/?d=n</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:04:37.000Z","msg":"請開名，邊間做得出唔怕認！"},{"pid":"cd0efe192a3104a71948ba7f80fd0316225a6f23","tid":2130313,"uid":1356